videos.headline: Northwestern strikes first
videos.description: Isaiah Bowser punches it in from the 2-yard line to give Northwestern a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Wildcats' QB keeps it himself for score
videos.description: Clayton Thorson fakes the handoff and takes it 13 yards himself for a score to give Northwestern a 13-7 lead over Minnesota.

videos.headline: Bowser finds end zone for second time
videos.description: Northwestern's Isaiah Bowser rushes up the middle for a 2-yard touchdown and his second score of the day.

videos.headline: Minnesota cuts into deficit with TD pass
videos.description: Tanner Morgan gets it to his receiver Tyler Johnson for a 6-yard score to cut Northwestern's lead to 24-14.
